# Reference only; this file intentionally contains no active assignments.
#
# The maintained Compose examples currently use no `env_file` directive or
# `${...}` substitutions, so copying this file to `.env` does not change the
# service. Put desired values under the service `environment` section (and use
# Core secret-file variables for credentials).

# Supported service-environment examples:
#   ZIGBEELENS_LOG_LEVEL=info  # debug | info | warning | error
#   TZ=UTC                     # process/log timezone; UI uses browser timezone
